documentation.author: Steve Wade
documentation.purpose:
This rule is designed to evoke when a patient chart is opened. The qualifiers for the rule are: • Location facility: SJH NOTE: 12/28/16 MPH added • Age: Greater than 65 • Health Plan: MEDICARE A, MEDICARE B, MEDICARE RAILROAD A, MEDICARE RAILROAD B • Risk Factor: High • Diagnosis: Multiple diagnosis, COPD related or Heart Failure related
The rule will place a “Home Care Telemonitoring” order/task unless there is an existing “Home Care Telemonitoring” order in Ordered or Completed status. The rule will place a “Consult to Home Health Care” order/task unless there is an existing “Consult to Home Health Care” order in Ordered or Completed status.
